          "block_id": 1,
          "block_order": 1
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "4.城市化问题",
          "block_bbox": [
            153,
            555,
            519,
            617
          ],
          "block_id": 2,
          "block_order": 2
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "(1)人口和城市的分布",
          "block_bbox": [
            220,
            661,
            751,
            725
          ],
          "block_id": 3,
          "block_order": 3
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "①特点：人口分布极不平衡，90%的人口居住在东部沿海地带，而且大城市十分集中。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            117,
            760,
            2030,
            917
          ],
          "block_id": 4,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "带来许多“城市病”：资源紧缺、交通拥挤、住房困难、就业紧张、污染严重、犯罪增多.\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            101,
            964,
            2041,
            1127
          ],
          "block_id": 5,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "解决措施：进行合理的城市规划、建立卫星城：城市中工业和人口向郊区分散;加强城市管理，重视保护和治理城市环境。\n",
          "block_bbox": [
            89,
            1176,
            2060,
            1345
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "paragraph_title",
          "block_content": "(2)主要城市：",
          "block_bbox": [
            217,
            1392,
            519,
            1452
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "圣保罗：经济中心，最大的城市和工业中心.",
          "block_bbox": [
            280,
            1491,
            1233,
            1555
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "里约热内卢：商业和金融中心，第二大城市.",
          "block_bbox": [
            283,
            1597,
            1235,
            1664
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 9
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "巴西利亚：政治中心，首都、是新建城市.",
          "block_bbox": [
            284,
            1703,
            1222,
            1764
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 10
        },
